link_metadata.description: “Today, a participant in a transnational repression scheme who worked to establish a secret police station in the middle of New York City on behalf of the national police force of the People’s Republic of China has pleaded guilty to conspiracy to act as an illegal agent.”
link_metadata.title: Chinese spy pleads guilty to running secret police base in Manhattan on behalf of CCP
